# =============================================================================
# Docker Ignore - Monorepo Root
# =============================================================================
# Excludes files from Docker build context to:
#   1. Speed up builds (smaller context)
#   2. Prevent sensitive data from being included
#   3. Avoid overwriting container-built artifacts
# =============================================================================

# Dependencies - rebuilt inside container
**/node_modules

# Build outputs - rebuilt inside container
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/out

# Development files
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# IDE and editor
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/.DS_Store

# Test files and coverage
**/coverage
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
**/vitest.config.ts
**/jest.config.*

# Git
.git
.gitignore
.gitmodules

# External submodules - not needed for container builds
external

# Documentation (not needed at runtime)
**/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md
**/docs
SITREP.md
infrastructure

# Docker files (prevent recursive context issues)
**/Dockerfile*
**/.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml

# CI/CD
.github

# Logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*

# TypeScript source maps (if generated)
**/*.map

# Next.js specific
**/.next
**/out

# Dashboard app (not needed for API gateway build)
# Uncomment if building dashboard separately
# apps/dashboard
